    "propose an interactive visualization tool called the \"What-if tool\" to increase awareness of the potential sources of discrimination in machine learning models [99].",
    "It provides an intuitive and user-friendly interface that allows users to explore the impact of various changes on the fairness and accuracy of machine learning models in real-time and visualize its outputs.",
